<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id="External_links">External links</h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Richard_Bulliet&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8" title="Edit section: External links"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130901135415/http://www.unesco.org/dialogue/en/bulliet.htm">Bulliet's address to the Dialogue among Civilizations</a>, United Nations, New York City, 5 September 2000</li></ul>
